---
// FAQ — 暗色 details 列表 + 旋转箭头（无横线）
// 节奏：vibeisland 640 容器 / 13px question / 13px answer 1.6
---

<!-- BEGIN: FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq section">
  <div class="container-faq">
    <div class="faq__header">
      <h2 class="faq__heading">
        <span data-i18n="faq.heading">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq__list">
      <details class="faq__item">
        <summary class="faq__summary">
          <span data-i18n="faq.q1">What services are supported?</span>
          <svg class="faq__chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__answer">
          <span data-i18n="faq.a1">We currently support GitHub, OpenAI, Claude, Vercel, and many more out of the box. You can also configure custom endpoints to track virtually anything.</span>
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq__item">
        <summary class="faq__summary">
          <span data-i18n="faq.q2">Is it secure?</span>
          <svg class="faq__chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__answer">
          <span data-i18n="faq.a2">Absolutely. Your API keys and data never leave your local machine. Quota Bar communicates directly with the service providers.</span>
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq__item">
        <summary class="faq__summary">
          <span data-i18n="faq.q3">Does it work on Windows?</span>
          <svg class="faq__chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__answer">
          <span data-i18n="faq.a3">No, Quota Bar is exclusively built for macOS to deeply integrate with the menu bar and deliver native performance.</span>
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq__item">
        <summary class="faq__summary">
          <span data-i18n="faq.q4">Is this a subscription?</span>
          <svg class="faq__chevron" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__answer">
          <span data-i18n="faq.a4">No! Quota Bar is a one-time purchase. You get lifetime access to the current features and all future minor updates.</span>
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- END: FAQ Section -->

<style>
  .faq__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);  /* 48px */
  }

  .faq__heading {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);  /* 24px — section 修饰标题 */
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq__heading {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);  /* 28px mobile */
    }
  }

  .faq__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);  /* 12px */
  }

  .faq__item {
    /* 无横线 */
  }

  .faq__summary {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);  /* 13px */
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;  /* 16px 0 */
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .faq__summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
  .faq__summary:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .faq__chevron {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: transform var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: var(--space-3);
  }
  .faq__item[open] .faq__chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .faq__answer {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);  /* 13px */
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
</style>